						<div class="postbody">What manifest? If you're using the build GGuy made, I can't help you since I haven't used it. If you're talking about the manifest used from the custom-gfx-hd branch, don't use that. It's experimental work intended to handle GBC sprites.<br /><br />I downloaded the 1.0 tarball from GB Enahnced's Google Code page, compiled that, and was able to dump and load tiles from SaGa. If you're doing anything that's not based on the 1.0 version from the Google Code page, that's likely the cause of the problem.</div>

