					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p147076">Re: Replacement Graphics in Shonumi's Game Boy Enhanced</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=147076&amp;sid=bae10347efc78eb9767015da694aa9ed#p147076"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Fri May 08, 2015 6:51 am&nbsp;</div></td>
